      "text": "Brake Master Power Negative Pressure Sensor Removal and Installation"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. Brake Master Power Negative Pressure Sensor Removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "706_3.0_jpn_11035974_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Remove the bracket (A). Disconnect the coupler (B). Disconnect the negative pressure tube (C)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "706_3.0_jpn_11035975_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "4",
      "text": "Remove the brake master power negative pressure sensor (A) together with the bracket (B). Remove the brake master power negative pressure sensor."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "2. Installation Precautions"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Installation is the reverse of the removal procedure."
    }
  ],
